      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Landscapes considered in the past or present as consecrated or important to a deity or a religion particularly including natural features, such as springs and caves. Also natural areas used for spiritual inspiration and to guide their contemplation of the divine.</Note_Text>
